    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please note: this game is short (~40 minutes)</strong><br>From the creator of The Man in the Park horror games and Lucky Numbers (horror novelette) comes Frog Legs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>Following a horrific accident during a routine game of hopping through lanes of traffic with your frog friends, you decide to go try to live normal frog lives and to never speak of that day again. Sounds good, right? The only problem is, sometimes the past has legs and catches up with you . . . </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOOMER SHOOTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/6ba2daad93d77c458fb2d7c9f77a6a5f.poster.avif?t=1752285940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/6ba2daad93d77c458fb2d7c9f77a6a5f.webm?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/6ba2daad93d77c458fb2d7c9f77a6a5f.mp4?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D ARCADE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/f475da22e5b017ff339b3786662e1180.poster.avif?t=1752285940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/f475da22e5b017ff339b3786662e1180.webm?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/f475da22e5b017ff339b3786662e1180.mp4?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D HORROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/e3b9f54367d01eed0265e6c3ddf9be6c.poster.avif?t=1752285940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/e3b9f54367d01eed0265e6c3ddf9be6c.webm?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734110/extras/e3b9f54367d01eed0265e6c3ddf9be6c.mp4?t=1752285940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can be completed in a single sitting (30-40min)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story-driven experience with a little horror, some action, and <strong>plenty</strong> of humor!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2D Arcade</strong> gameplay reminiscent of the classics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D First-Person</strong> <strong>puzzles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Boomer Shooter FPS action</strong> with a <strong>shotgun</strong> and <strong>BFG (Big Froggin' Gun)!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Note: This is not a full boomer shooter / FPS game. That is only part of the game.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An ensemble of characters you'll never frog-get!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-save on each new level for convenience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a story-driven horror action game with 2D and 3D gameplay,<strong> Frog Legs</strong> has a little bit of everything. So grab a cup of flies (or your preferred snack), and hop into this story-driven horror action experience designed to be completed in a single session! </p>",
